{
  "stem": "6924.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But after-- me, after a couple months that I-- and I didn't have anything what to do, I didn't have any experience in anything practical, so I-- I got-- I took a course in Lemberg.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Lwow is the name of it, the Polish name, Lwow.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they-- I finished that course, a six-month course, that for the Russian.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they send me to work in a town-- it's actually a village-- very close to the new Russian-German border.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I worked there until the war broke out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when I left in 1940 for-- for Lwow, for that course, that's the last time I saw my family.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because when the war broke out in '41, I was already-- I was together with the-- with the Russians, and we were ordered to leave the place.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the Germans were right on the border, and we supposed to go east to Russia.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I was on the truck with other workers, office workers, going to Russia.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But on my mind, I just didn't feel good, that I felt I'm going to-- here I am.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'm going to go to Russia, save myself, and I'm going to leave my family.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I just didn't feel right about it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I felt that I couldn't do it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the first chance when the truck stopped in Brody, I made up my--",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Brody, B-R-O-D-Y.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's a town in Galicia close to Zlotchov.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I made up my mind that I am not going to go to Russia, that I'm going to get off the truck and try to get home to my hometown.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But the closest town was Zlotchov.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I knew I have an uncle, an aunt living in Zlotchov.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were about 30 kilometers from the place the truck stopped to Zlotchov.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
